    {
      "id": "1cc6efd3-5ce7-4265-8257-a40795563352",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $a,m,n\\ \\in \\N^{*}$, $a\\ge 2$, et $d = (a^n - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a,m,n\\ \\in \\N^{*}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\ge 2\\)</span>, et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(d = (a^n - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "279156fe-095f-4bb5-9c8b-2321cc9a4e21",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $n = qm + r$ la division euclidienne de $n$ par $m$.\n      D{\\'e}montrer que $a^n \\equiv a^r (\\mathrm{mod}\\, {a^m - 1})$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n = qm + r\\)</span> la division euclidienne de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(m\\)</span>. D<span>é</span>montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^n \\equiv a^r (\\mathrm{mod}\\, {a^m - 1})\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "431473d5-e805-443a-889f-3fa9f076c810",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a^m - 1\\mid (a^{qm} - 1)a^r = a^n - a^r$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^m - 1\\mid (a^{qm} - 1)a^r = a^n - a^r\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "eda8cf3d-efd5-4cae-99a3-8c2f51780162",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire que $d = (a^r - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)$,\n      puis $d = a^{(n \\wedge m)} - 1$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(d = (a^r - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)\\)</span>, puis <span class=\"math inline\">\\(d = a^{(n \\wedge m)} - 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "250136b9-9d45-40d5-a86f-dda8cfbee06d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$A\\wedge(AQ+R) = A\\wedge R$.\n      Algorithme d'Euclide sur les exposants de $a$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\wedge(AQ+R) = A\\wedge R\\)</span>. Algorithme d’Euclide sur les exposants de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6578a97c-589e-4f27-bb0c-d5cb3ae8f290",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "A quelle condition $a^m - 1$ divise-t-il $a^n-1$ ?",
        "html": "<p>A quelle condition <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^m - 1\\)</span> divise-t-il <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^n-1\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b3b5c02f-8d5c-41b3-a1d0-2dc5ded25d8a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "ssi $m\\mid n$.",
        "html": "<p>ssi <span class=\"math inline\">\\(m\\mid n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
